---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>About SynergyFlow</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Pioneering the future of workplace collaboration through innovative,
        AI-driven solutions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="about-text">
        At SynergyFlow, we're passionate about revolutionizing the way organizations
        collaborate. We don't build software &mdash; we build the future of work. Our
        mission: to empower teams worldwide with innovative, AI-driven solutions that
        unlock unprecedented levels of productivity and foster meaningful collaboration
        across every facet of the modern workplace.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Journey</h2>
      <p class="about-text">
        Founded in 2023, SynergyFlow was born from a simple yet profound realization
        &mdash; in today's rapidly evolving digital landscape, businesses need more
        than just tools. They need a holistic ecosystem. Not a platform. A partner.
      </p>
      <p class="about-text">
        I started this company because I believed in something bigger. I saw the
        challenges teams face. I understood the frustration of disconnected workflows.
        I knew there had to be a better way. You might feel the same frustration
        in your own organization &mdash; the manual processes, the lost productivity,
        the missed opportunities for synergy.
      </p>
      <p class="about-text">
        Our journey has been nothing short of transformative. From our humble beginnings
        as a small team of passionate innovators, we've grown into a world-class
        organization serving thousands of clients globally. But growth isn't the story
        here &mdash; impact is. Furthermore, we continue to push the boundaries of
        what's possible in the realm of workplace collaboration technology.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="section-title">Meet the Team</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Our diverse team of industry experts brings a wealth of experience to the table.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-grid team-grid">
        <div class="card team-card">
          <h3>Alexandra Chen</h3>
          <p class="team-role">Chief Executive Officer</p>
          <p>
            A visionary leader passionate about empowering teams. For Alexandra,
            leadership isn't about authority &mdash; it's about enabling others. She aims
            to leverage her 15 years of experience navigating the intricate landscape
            of technology innovation to drive meaningful change.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card team-card">
          <h3>Marcus Rivera</h3>
          <p class="team-role">Chief Technology Officer</p>
          <p>
            With a robust background in cutting-edge software architecture, Marcus
            brings a nuanced understanding of scalable systems. He doesn't write code
            &mdash; he crafts solutions. His meticulous approach seeks to ensure every
            line of code delivers maximum value.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card team-card">
          <h3>Dr. Priya Sharma</h3>
          <p class="team-role">Head of AI</p>
          <p>
            A thought leader in the realm of artificial intelligence, Dr. Sharma's
            groundbreaking research has been instrumental in shaping our innovative
            approach to leveraging machine learning for enterprise solutions. For her,
            AI isn't a technology &mdash; it's a responsibility.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-alt values-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h2 class="section-title">Our Core Values</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">
            These values serve as the cornerstone of everything we do.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-item">
            <h3>Innovation at Our Core</h3>
            <p>Innovation isn't something we do &mdash; it's who we are. We seek to constantly push boundaries, leveraging cutting-edge technologies to deliver transformative solutions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <h3>Customer-Centric Excellence</h3>
            <p>We aim to put our customers at the heart of every decision, fostering meaningful partnerships that drive mutual success.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <h3>Transparent Collaboration</h3>
            <p>We try to maintain open and honest communication, building trust through transparency in everything we endeavour to accomplish.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <h3>Sustainable Growth</h3>
            <p>Success isn't a destination &mdash; it's a direction. We believe in building for the long term, creating scalable solutions that grow alongside our clients' evolving needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 750px;
  }

  .team-role {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .values-section {
    margin: 3rem -1.5rem 0;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
</style>
